        <p style="color: #0095ca;font-size: 16px; margin:0px;"><b>Terms & Conditions</b></p>
        <p style="color: #333;font-size: 14px; margin:0px 0px 5px 0px;"><b>This receipt is computer generated and only valid at  Counters.</b></p>
        <p style="color: #333;font-size: 16px; margin:0px;"><b>Pay Radiance</b></p>
        <p style="color: #333;font-size: 14px; margin:0px;"><b>Regd. & Corp. Office:</b></p>*@



</div>
<div class="text-center">
    <button id="printPageButton" onclick="window.print();" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:fit-content;">Print</button>
</div>
